{"title":"","slug":"VS-2017-Hello-World","url":"http://yoursite.com/VS-2017-Hello-World","date":"2018-01-30T09:23:23.960Z","updated":"2018-01-30T00:44:02.418Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<h1 id=\"如何在-VS-2017-中输出-“Hello-World”\"><a href=\"#如何在-VS-2017-中输出-“Hello-World”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如何在 VS 2017 中输出 “Hello World”\"></a>如何在 VS 2017 中输出 “Hello World”</h1><p>##1.下载安装 VS2017<br>根据自己的需求下载 <a href=\"https://www.visualstudio.com/zh-hans/?rr=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baidu.com%2Flink%3Furl%3DnhXYuxOUqhnYk6qG9TznWDLLPEqFQLfy6dCzW7fn44e9K_7SiP4wXhXBh4SSook4%26wd%3D%26eqid%3Ddc4eeda300001a94000000065a6f0dc2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Visual Studio</a></p>\n<p>安装过程略</p>\n<p>##2.创建文件</p>\n<p>###创建项目文件<br>选择<strong>文件</strong>-&gt;<strong>新建</strong>-&gt;<strong>项目</strong>创建项目<br><img src=\"vs_1.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>右侧<strong>已安装</strong>下选择<strong>Visual C++</strong>,<strong>常规</strong>,选择<strong>空项目</strong><br><img src=\"vs_2.png\" alt=\"\"><br>项目<strong>名称</strong>和<strong>位置</strong>可以自定义，点击<strong>确定</strong>。</p>\n<p><img src=\"vs_3.png\" alt=\"\"><br>在菜单栏选择<strong>视图</strong>窗口，打开<strong>解决方案资源管理器</strong></p>\n<p>###设置项目属性<br>在 Visual Studio 中选择<strong>项目</strong>菜单栏，选择最后一项<strong>属性</strong>，或者直接右击左侧<strong>解决方案资源管理器</strong>中的<strong>Project1</strong>，选择最后一项<strong>属性</strong>，<br>弹出下图所示的对话框<br><img src=\"vs_6.png\" alt=\"\"><br>左侧选择<strong>配置属性</strong>-&gt;<strong>链接器</strong>-&gt;<strong>系统</strong>，右侧选择<strong>子系统</strong>，下拉菜单中选择<strong>控制台(/SUBSYSTEM:CONSOLE)</strong>,点击<strong>确定</strong>完成。</p>\n<p>###创建源文件<br>回到Visual Studio<br><img src=\"vs_4.png\" alt=\"\"><br>在右侧<strong>解决方案资源管理器</strong>中，右键<strong>源文件</strong>-&gt;<strong>添加</strong>-&gt;<strong>新建</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"vs_5.png\" alt=\"\"><br>在弹出的窗口中右侧选择<strong>Visual C++</strong> -&gt; <strong>C++文件(.cpp)</strong>,建议讲文件名称改为<em>HelloWorld.cpp</em>,位置为默认位置。单击<strong>确定</strong>                   </p>\n<p>##3.输入代码<br>在下图所示的窗口中输入代码<br><img src=\"vs_7.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span><span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"built_in\">std</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">std</span>::<span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"Hello World\"</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">std</span>::<span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"Hello World\"</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>##4.编译并运行<br>在 Visual Studio 的菜单栏中选择<strong>生成</strong>-&gt;<strong>生成解决方案</strong><br><img src=\"vs_9.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>下图<strong>输出</strong>窗口中应表明没有错误，否则检查代码是否有误。<br><img src=\"vs_10.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>确认代码无误后，菜单栏中选择<strong>调试</strong>-&gt;<strong>开始执行(不调试)</strong>,或者按下<strong>Ctrl</strong>+<strong>F5</strong>。<br><img src=\"vs_11.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>弹出下图所示窗口，表明输出成功，其中第一行是用 <strong>Static静态成员函数</strong> 输出 “<strong>Hello World</strong>“,下一行是用 <strong>iostream标准输入输出流</strong> 中的 <strong>COUT</strong> 输出<br><img src=\"vs_12.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"My First Blog","slug":"My-First-Blog"},"next":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world"}}